room_title: Escape room "Blackout" by Race 2 Xcape in Springfield (MO)
room_address: 4560 S. Campbell, Ste L128 Springfield, MO 65810
room_description: Your colleague, a world-renowned photographer, went missing under mysterious circumstances. Before his disappearance, he took a priceless photo of the elusive Sumatran Orangutan. Using the clues he left behind, find the photo before it falls into the wrong hands, and get out of his darkroom before your time runs out!
